<div class="post">
<div class="inner" id="msg_1111817"><span style="font-size: 12pt;" class="bbc_size"><span style="color: red;" class="bbc_color"><strong>大脚野人Sasquatch</strong></span></span><br><hr /><em>这种高大，魁梧，毛茸茸的类人生物挥舞着大树枝，步态酷似猿猴。</em><br><hr /><span style="color: brown;" class="bbc_color"><span style="font-size: 10pt;" class="bbc_size"><strong>大脚野人，CR2</strong></span></span><br><span style="color: navy;" class="bbc_color"><strong>XP 600</strong></span><br>绝对中立 中型类人生物（大脚亚种）<br><span style="color: navy;" class="bbc_color"><strong>先攻</strong></span> +2；<span style="color: navy;" class="bbc_color"><strong>感官：</strong></span>黑暗视觉60尺，昏暗视觉，灵敏嗅觉；<span style="color: navy;" class="bbc_color"><strong>察觉 </strong></span>+5<br><hr /><strong><span style="color: green;" class="bbc_color"><span style="font-size: 10pt;" class="bbc_size">防御</span></span></strong><br><hr />AC 14，碰触 12，措手不及 12 （+2敏捷，+2天生）<br>HP 22（3d8+9）<br>强韧 +4，反射 +5，意志 +1<br><hr /><span style="font-size: 10pt;" class="bbc_size"><strong><span style="color: green;" class="bbc_color">攻击</span></strong></span><br><hr /><span style="color: navy;" class="bbc_color"><strong>速度</strong></span>40尺<br><span style="color: navy;" class="bbc_color"><strong>近战：</strong></span>木棒+8（1d6+9）或挥击+8（1d4+9）<br><span style="color: navy;" class="bbc_color"><strong>远程：</strong></span>投石+5（1d4+9）<br><span style="color: navy;" class="bbc_color"><strong>特殊攻击：</strong></span>投石（120尺）<br><hr /><strong><span style="color: green;" class="bbc_color"><span style="font-size: 10pt;" class="bbc_size">数据</span></span></strong>[/size]<br><hr /><span style="color: navy;" class="bbc_color"><strong>力量</strong></span> 22，<strong><span style="color: navy;" class="bbc_color">敏捷 </span></strong>15，<span style="color: navy;" class="bbc_color"><strong>体质</strong></span> 16，<span style="color: navy;" class="bbc_color"><strong>智力</strong></span> 9，<span style="color: navy;" class="bbc_color"><strong>感知</strong></span> 10，<span style="color: navy;" class="bbc_color"><strong>魅力</strong></span> 11<br><span style="color: navy;" class="bbc_color"><strong>BAB</strong></span> +2；<span style="color: navy;" class="bbc_color"><strong>CMB</strong></span> +8；<span style="color: navy;" class="bbc_color"><strong>CMD</strong></span> 20<br><span style="color: navy;" class="bbc_color"><strong>专长：</strong></span>自给自足（Self-Sufficient），技能专攻（隐匿）（Skill Focus (Stealth)）<br><span style="color: navy;" class="bbc_color"><strong>技能：</strong></span>医疗+2，察觉+5，隐匿+10（+14在森林区域），生存+10；种族调整+4察觉，+4隐匿（+8在森林区域），+4生存<br><span style="color: navy;" class="bbc_color"><strong>语言：</strong></span>大脚语（Sasquatch）<br><span style="color: navy;" class="bbc_color"><strong>特殊能力：</strong></span>刺鼻气味（pungency），穿林步（woodland stride）<br><hr /><span style="font-size: 10pt;" class="bbc_size"><span style="color: green;" class="bbc_color"><strong>生态背景</strong></span></span><br><hr /><span style="color: navy;" class="bbc_color"><strong>环境：</strong></span>温带或寒带的森林<br><span style="color: navy;" class="bbc_color"><strong>组织：</strong></span>单独，成对或家庭（3-7）<br><span style="color: navy;" class="bbc_color"><strong>财宝：</strong></span>标准<br><hr /><span style="font-size: 10pt;" class="bbc_size"><span style="color: green;" class="bbc_color"><strong>特殊能力</strong></span></span><br><hr /><span style="color: navy;" class="bbc_color"><strong>刺鼻气味（pungency，Ex）：</strong></span>大脚野人的气味非常的强烈，通过灵敏嗅觉可以在正常距离的2倍远发现它。<br><br><span style="color: navy;" class="bbc_color"><strong>穿林步（Woodland Stride, Ex）：</strong></span>大脚野人能以正常速度通过任何灌木丛（例如自然的荆棘丛，石南丛，茂密的灌木丛，以及其他类似地形），并且不会受到任何伤害或其他损害。然而，如果上述地形是由魔法造成以阻碍移动，仍会影响大脚野人。<br><br>难以捉摸的大脚野人赢得了神秘的声誉。他们生活在人烟稀少的森林中，避免与其他类人生物面对面接触，只有在他们受到威胁，领土被侵占或是他们必须保护自己的后辈时才会变得暴力。<br>除他们自己的用具外，大脚野人家族非常满足于生活在深林之中，除了地面上的大面积足迹外，几乎没有不会留下任何痕迹。尽管脚相当大，但是它们却是难以置信的潜藏生物，能够以惊人的优雅和速度穿越森林。<br>某种程度上破坏了隐匿特征的另一个特征是它们独特的气味，一种刺鼻的麝香，即使大脚野人本身隐藏的很好，通常也十分明显。<br>大脚野人是难以捉摸的，以至于即使是在一个龙和海怪都真实存在的世界中，许多城市中的学者仍保持怀疑，认为缺少大脚野人的巢穴或痕迹以证明他们是否存在。实际上，大脚野人与大多数类人生物所期望的相比，更加简单高效的与自然和谐相处。对于一个大脚野人来说，森林中的死角是一个完美的家。当大脚野人死后，其亲属会费劲将尸体深埋，并掩盖墓地的所有痕迹，以保护残骸免受拾荒者和邪灵的侵害。大脚野人的语言是一种相对复杂的语言，将发声，嚎叫和敲击声（用棍棒或石头敲击固体表面（如树或巨石）的行为）混合在一起，混入森林的声音中。<br>大脚野人高8英尺，重570磅。农村人经常为这些生物起昵称，例如野人，臭鼬猿，也许最流行的就是大脚怪。<br><br><div style="margin:20px; margin-top:5px"><div class="smallfont" style="margin-bottom:2px"><b>剧透</b> - &nbsp;<i> </i>: <input type="button" value="顯示" style="width:60px;font-size:10px;margin:0px;padding:0px;" onClick="if (this.parentNode.parentNode.getElementsByTagName('div')[1].getElementsByTagName('div')[0].style.display != '') { this.parentNode.parentNode.getElementsByTagName('div')[1].getElementsByTagName('div')[0].style.display = ''; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;this.innerText = ''; this.value = '隐藏'; } else { this.parentNode.parentNode.getElementsByTagName('div')[1].getElementsByTagName('div')[0].style.display = 'none'; this.innerText = ''; this.value = '显示'; }"></div><div class="alt2" style="margin: 0px; padding: 6px; border: 1px inset;"><div style="display: none;">Sasquatch<br>Tall, burly, and hairy, this humanoid creature wields a large tree branch for a club and has a swinging, apelike gait.<br>SASQUATCH CR 2<br>XP 600<br>N Medium humanoid (sasquatch)<br>Init +2; Senses darkvision 60 ft., low-light vision, scent;<br>Perception +5<br>DEFENSE<br>AC 14, touch 12, flat-footed 12 (+2 Dex, +2 natural)<br>hp 22 (3d8+9)<br>Fort +4, Ref +5, Will +1<br>OFFENSE<br>Speed 40 ft.<br>Melee club +8 (1d6+9) or slam +8 (1d4+9)<br>Ranged rock +5 (1d4+9)<br>Special Attacks rock throwing (120 ft.)<br>STATISTICS<br>Str 22, Dex 15, Con 16, Int 9, Wis 10, Cha 11<br>Base Atk +2; CMB +8; CMD 20<br>Feats Self-Sufficient, Skill Focus (Stealth)<br>Skills Heal +2, Perception +5, Stealth +10 (+14 in forested areas), Survival +10; Racial Modifiers +4 Perception, +4 Stealth (+8 in forested areas), +4 Survival<br>Languages Sasquatch<br>SQ pungency, woodland stride<br>ECOLOGY<br>Environment temperate or cold forests<br>Organization solitary, pair, or family (3–7)<br>Treasure standard<br>SPECIAL ABILITIES<br>Pungency (Ex) A sasquatch’s odor is quite powerful, and can be detected at twice the normal distance by scent.<br>Woodland Stride (Ex) A sasquatch can move through any sort of undergrowth (such as natural thorns, briars, overgrown areas, and similar terrain) at normal speed and without taking damage or suffering any other impairment.<br>Undergrowth that has been magically manipulated to impede movement still affects the sasquatch.<br><br><br>The elusive sasquatches earn their mysterious reputation rightly; they live in unpopulated forests and avoid confrontations with humanoids, only becoming violent when they feel threatened, when their territory is encroached upon, or when they feel they must protect their young. Left to their own devices, sasquatch families are perfectly content to live their lives in the deep woods, leaving behind little to no trace of their passing save for the periodic big footprint in the ground.<br>Despite their considerable bulk, sasquatches are incredibly stealthy creatures, capable of moving through forests in particular with astonishing grace and efficiency.<br>The one trait that somewhat undermines sasquatches’ stealth is their distinctive odor—a pungent, musky scent that is often noticeable even when the hidden sasquatches themselves are not apparent.<br>The elusiveness of sasquatches is such that even in a world where dragons and sea monsters are real, many urban scholars doubt the existence of the creatures, citing the lack of evidence of sasquatch lairs or remains as proof of their nonexistence. In truth, sasquatches are simply far more efficient at living in harmony with nature than most humanoids could ever hope to be. To a sasquatch, a deadfall in a forest makes a perfectly fine home. When a sasquatch dies, its kin take pains to bury the body deep and hide all trace of the gravesite to protect the remains from scavengers and evil spirits alike. The sasquatch tongue is a relatively complex language that mixes vocalizations, howls, and “knocking”—the act of striking a solid surface (like a tree or boulder) with a club or stone—and thus tends to blend in with the ambient sounds of a forest.<br>A sasquatch is 8 feet tall and weighs 570 pounds. Rural populaces often have fond nicknames for these creatures, such as wild men, skunk apes, and perhaps most popularly, simply bigfoot.</div></div></div><img src="https://z3.ax1x.com/2021/05/07/g3RJt1.png" alt="" class="bbc_img"/></div>
</div>
